» Property Consultant – The First Group – Dubai Jobs
Posted on 05 May 2014. Tags: , , , , ,
The First Group Company is looking for highly motivated property investment consultants to join our winning team. We are looking for Russian,
English and Arabic speakers with a full basic understanding of the English language.
Job Summary:
As a property investment consultant with The First Group,
you will be contacting high profile and pre-qualify clients to discuss investment opportunities in one of the hottest cities in the world. Expand company’s portfolio by generating maximum net sales volume while maintaining a professional and ethical representation of the company.
What to expect: Excellent earning potential,
base salary,
excellent commission structure,
health benefits,
cash incentives,
company loyalty programs,
extensive brand/sales Training, 22 days of paid vacation and more.
Job Details
Date Posted:
2014-05-04
Job Location:
Dubai, United Arab Emirates
Job Role:
Sales
Company Industry:
Real Estate
Preferred Candidate
Career Level:
Entry Level
Degree:
High school or equivalent
